T02D2351:5b-1: ba santi ti la ka do ha g'i ti ka n'a ma /
T02D2351:5b-3: dpyid kyi thig le do ha mdzod kyi glu zhes bya ba /
T02D2351:5b-4: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2351:5b-5: se bhu sku gsum la sogs kyi //
T02D2351:5b-6: sos ka'i me tog mthong ba yi //
T02D2351:5b-7: gzhon nu bdag ni myos par 'gyur //
T02D2351:5b-8: he ru ka la chags pa yis //
T02D2351:5b-9: sos ka'i dang po dang po 'dir //
T02D2351:5b-10: khyod kyis bdag ni bsrung bar mdzod //
T02D2351:5b-11: gdung bas 'gum par ma mdzad cig / me tog aam bha ka ru na //
T02D2351:5b-12: dri bsung ldan pas dgyes par 'gyur //
T02D2351:5b-13: sha ris pas ni brdungs pas brdungs //
T02D2351:5b-14: me mar khur nas tsanda l'i //
T02D2351:5b-15: ri mo bdag la 'bab bo zhes //
T02D2351:5b-16: ka na pa ni gshegs par re //
T02D2351:5b-17: so ga'i dang po dpyid dus la //
T02D2351:5b-18: khyod kyis bdag ni bsrung bar mdzod //
T02D2351:5b-19: gdung bas 'gum par ma mdzad cig / phyogs bcur bltas na bdag gis ni //
T02D2351:5b-20: khyod las gzhan ni mthong ba med //
T02D2351:5b-21: gdung ba'i mo yis bdag gis ni //
T02D2351:5b-22: bdag gi lus kyang bsam pa med //
T02D2351:5b-23: rnal 'byor ma brgyad las bzhi ni //
T02D2351:5b-24: bdag cag gsol ba btab pa yis //
T02D2351:5b-25: bcom ldan 'das ni bzhengs par mdzod //
T02D2351:5b-26: dpyid kyi thig le do ha mdzod kyi glu zhes
T02D2351:5b-27: bya ba slob dpon nag po nas brgyud pa slob
